    "rich_text_GbXVUF": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_XhCLHT": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>ORI SSM Chevy Silverado 2500HD Packages</strong>",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "enable_highlight_text_color": true,
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_color": "#5683c2"
          }
        },
        "text_CfcJd4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2><strong>AN AUSTRALIAN FIRST: The Ultimate Silverado 2500HD Build — No Truck License Required!</strong></h2><p>If you’ve been holding off on building a true, uncompromised Super-Truck because you refused to cross into truck-license territory, <strong>the game just changed.</strong></p><p>For the very first time in Australia, you can build the Silverado of your dreams without upgrading your license.</p><p>Thanks to our exclusive, newly engineered, and <strong>Federally Approved Second Stage Manufacture (SSM) packages</strong>, we are shattering the limits of what a standard-license vehicle can be. You can now run up to a massive <strong>6.5-inch lift</strong> on <strong>37-inch tyres</strong> while keeping your Silverado 2500HD classified strictly under 4.5 tonnes (NB1).</p><h3><strong>What Does This Mean For You?</strong></h3><p>It means you no longer have to compromise. You get:</p><ul><li><strong>The Monster Stance:</strong> Turn heads and dominate the road with an aggressive, towering footprint.</li><li><strong>Uncompromising Ground Clearance:</strong> Tackle any terrain Australia has to offer without a second thought.</li><li><strong>100% Street Legal:</strong> Drive the biggest, baddest truck on the market using your standard Australian car license.</li></ul><h3><strong>⚠️ The \"Pre-Rego\" Golden Rule</strong></h3><p>There is only one catch to making this dream a reality: <strong>It must be done Pre-Registration.</strong></p><p>To legally bake these extreme modifications directly into the truck's federal compliance plate under the SSM scheme, the vehicle <em>must</em> be built and certified before it is registered for the very first time.</p><p><strong>Why does this matter?</strong> It means you get to skip the endless red tape. You completely avoid the aftermarket engineering nightmares, the police defects, and the insurance headaches.</p><p>You simply choose the stage that suits your dream truck, and we put you in touch with an ORI-authorised installer. You choose your wheels and tyres with them, and then <strong>BOOM</strong>—your build starts. You'll take delivery of a fully compliant, fully insured super-truck that you can legally drive Australia-wide.</p><p><strong>Don't settle for standard. Be the first.</strong> Secure your Pre-Rego allocation today and build the ultimate Silverado 2500HD.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
