    "image_with_text_rJkhtG": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_DWKAtN": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "subheading": "Stage 5 : $21,999* - Installed & Engineered"
          }
        },
        "heading_R6xiqM": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>Stage 5: 6.5\" Summit Spec</strong>",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "enable_highlight_text_color": false,
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_YBjh6X": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Best for:</strong> The owner who wants the absolute maximum height available on a heavy-duty torsion setup. If you want that towering \"big truck\" presence that is 100% legal, the Stage 5 package delivers a massive BDS 6.5\" system with Fox 2.5 Performance Elite shocks, allowing you to run 37\" tyres fully legal on a standard car licence under our pre-rego SSM (Second Stage Manufacture) approval.</p><ul><li><strong>Lift Height:</strong> 6.5 Inches</li><li><strong>Tyre Size:</strong> Engineered specifically for 37-inch tyres.</li><li><strong>Suspension Tech:</strong> Utilises a heavy-duty <strong>BDS 6.5\" High-Clearance Kit</strong>, featuring a full replacement subframe drop and upgraded replacement steering knuckles to keep your factory steering geometry perfectly intact at the massive 6.5-inch ride height. ORI also includes the premium <strong>BDS upper control arms</strong> to give the front end a completely integrated, high-end look while retaining the robust factory torsion bar setup.</li><li><strong>Shock Configuration:</strong> <strong>Fox 2.5 Performance Elite Series Shocks</strong> <em>(front and rear)</em> featuring remote reservoirs and adjustable damping. You can literally dial in the ride with a simple clicker—soften it up for a plush highway cruise, or firm it up for control on the tracks.</li><li><strong>Extras:</strong> We also include colour-coded <strong>Husky Extenda Flares</strong> and <strong>ORI Metal mud flap brackets with rubber</strong> to ensure your vehicle is completely compliant and federally approved.</li><li><strong>What's Not Included:</strong> Just your wheels and tyres! All you need to do is pick your style. We have already set the specific wheel offsets required to keep the build federally compliant, so there is no need to stress about load ratings or legality.</li><li><strong>CHV-2500-STAGE-5-NB1</strong></li></ul>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "subheading_DWKAtN",
        "heading_R6xiqM",
